These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: ebony, black, white, chestnut
The people have 4 different jobs:  librarian, teacher, paramedic, journalist
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, ice-hockey, lacrosse, water-polo
House: art-deco, wooden, victorian, farmhouse
 1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is not to the right of the person who's sport is cycling##8
 2. the art-deco house is not to the left of the art-deco house##8
 3. the farmhouse house is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who's sport is cycling is not to the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##8
 5. the art-deco house is not to the right of the art-deco house##8
 6. the paramedic is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 7. the person who likes black is somewhere to the right of the person who likes ebony##5
 8. the journalist is between the wooden house and the person who's sport is ice-hockey##2
 9. the farmhouse house is the paramedic##1
10. the farmhouse house is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1
11. the person who likes white is on the left or right of the librarian##3
12. the person who likes chestnut is somewhere to the right of the person who likes black##5
13. the paramedic is not to the left of the farmhouse house##8
14. the person who likes black is the victorian house##1
15. the person who likes black is not the person who's sport is ice-hockey##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Color         | ebony     | black   | chestnut | white |
| Job   | teacher | journalist   | librarian   | paramedic  |
| Sport         | ice-hockey  | lacrosse  | water-polo  | cycling |
| House     | art-deco    | victorian | wooden     | farmhouse    |

