.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
House: modern, gothic-revival, art-deco, townhouse
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, march, may, july
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, dunhill, game, prince
4 different pets are kept: dog, frog, goldfish, rabbit
 1. the game-smoker is between the owner of the dog and the dunhill-smoker##2
 2. the gothic-revival house is not to the right of the owner of the frog##8
 3. the gothic-revival house is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in october##3
 4. the modern house is not to the right of the owner of the rabbit##8
 5. the owner of the dog is not to the left of the dunhill-smoker##8
 6. the person who's birthday is in july is not to the right of the townhouse house##8
 7. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the left of the owner of the rabbit##5
 8. the owner of the goldfish is in an odd position##4
 9. the alhambra-smoker is the owner of the frog##1
10. the game-smoker is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3
11. the owner of the dog is not to the left of the game-smoker##8
12. the townhouse house is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
13. the prince-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in march##5
14. the dunhill-smoker is on the left or right of the game-smoker##3
15. the modern house is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
17. the modern house is not to the right of the dunhill-smoker##8
18. the person who's birthday is in march is not to the right of the owner of the frog##8
19. the townhouse house is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
| House      | modern | art-deco | townhouse  | gothic-revival  |
| Birthday          | july     | march | october | may  |
| Cigar   | dunhill    | game  | prince | alhambra |
| Pet           | goldfish | rabbit | dog    | frog  |

