.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, card-games, skydiving, sudoku
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, car, jet-ski, bike
There 4 different types of food: cherry, papaya, cucumber, apple
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, canasta, billiard, go
 1. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
 2. the person who's hobby is card-games is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##5
 3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere to the left of the person driving the bike##5
 4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere to the right of the person eating cherry##5
 5. the person playing billiard is not to the right of the person driving the quad-bike##8
 6. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not to the left of the person driving the jet-ski##8
 7. the person eating cucumber is in an odd position##4
 8. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
 9. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person driving the car##1
10. the person playing canasta is on the far right##1
11. the person driving the quad-bike is not to the left of the person eating papaya##8
12. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the person playing canasta##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | camping    | sudoku   | skydiving | card-games |
| Transport   | quad-bike     | jet-ski  | bike   | car      |
| Food   | papaya | cherry    | cucumber      | apple       |
| Game         | billiard    | mah-jongg | go   | canasta    |

