.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-4::.
There 4 different types of food: apple, banana, cucumber, plum
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, july, february, may
There are 4 different favourite colors: orange, white, blood-red, green
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, soul, punk, classical
 1. the person who's birthday is in february is not the person who likes orange##6
 2. the person who likes green is on the left or right of the fan of punk##3
 3. the person eating plum is the person who likes blood-red##1
 4. the person eating banana is between the person who likes orange and the person who likes white##2
 5. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3
 6. the fan of salsa is not to the right of the person eating banana##8
 7. the person who's birthday is in may is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's birthday is in february is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in september##5
 9. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who likes green##1
10. the person who likes white is the fan of salsa##1
11. the fan of soul is not to the right of the person eating apple##8
12. the person who likes orange is on the left or right of the fan of soul##3
13. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
14. the person who likes white is on the left or right of the fan of soul##3
15. the person who's birthday is in september is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |         2          |    3    |    4     |
| Food    | cucumber    | banana             | apple   | plum     |
| Birthday   | september | february            | may | july    |
| Color     | white | green | orange  | blood-red |
| Music-Genre   | salsa  | soul               | punk  | classical   |

